  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="44912053">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lilopeng/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u39540263-3.jpg" alt="Lilopeng" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44912053/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44912053/" class="">第59页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lilopeng/" class=" " title="Lilopeng">Lilopeng</a>
                (无病无灾不痛不痒)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44912053">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">你們兩個不是今日頭疼，就是明日牙疼，要麼是沒話尋著話說，一說話又掐得像一對公雞，你們知道這是為啥嗎，不是你們吵架，是肝和肝吵架，肝火都太旺麼。啥還能生病？一是心要放坦，既來之心安之，精神放鬆。二是多做些好事。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-15 12:43</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
